title: Hardcore - Hardstyle - Dance
description:
This is my personal collection of Hardcore, Hardstyle and dance music. It mostly contains dutch Dj&#039;s such as Angerfist, The Prophet, Dj Duro, Headhunterz, Neophyte (no early rave) and Showtek.

The collection contains estimately 40% Hardcore, 40% Hardstyle and 20% Dance music. I listen to this music everyday and I hope you guys can enjoy it just as much as I do.

Happy listening.
